Commands
Special Key presses:

Cntrl-Alt-space  freezes/unfreezes an experiment. When an expt is "frozen" the stimulus sequence is no longer incremented, so that the same stimulus is shown over and over.

Cntrl-Alt-+ increments the stimulus sequence
Cntrl-Alt-+ decrements the stimulus sequence

Special Commands (all start with \):

\quit exits
\saveim  saves an image of the last frame in the expt.